title: Railworks TS2014 DT LNER B12 Loco
description:
This is version 3 of DT LNER B12

Pack Features:

- Quick Drive Compatible

- Custom Cab

- Custom Sounds from Steam Sounds Supreme

- Variety of Liveries: Pre and Post War LNER Apple Green, Wartime Black, BR Lined Black, BR Experimental Blue

- Advanced Scripted effects

- Reverser Lock, Reverser Slip, Ejector, Sand, Slip and more Particle effects, Cab glow light effect, Custom Lamp system, Custom Disc system, Changeable smoke effect depending on engine condition.




Please support the developers and buy some of their content if you can afford it.


Please use the email address or the facebook fanpage for requests, questions and also if you want to share an addon with the community which we will post on your behalf.

If you would like to contribute, please read the Readme.pdf.
